---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="AI Receptionist — LeadFair"
  description="Never miss a call again. An AI phone agent that answers calls, books appointments, and handles common questions for your business 24/7."
  headline="Never Miss Another Call"
  subheadline="An AI phone agent that answers your business calls, books appointments, handles common questions, and sends you a summary — 24 hours a day, 7 days a week."
  accentColor="primary"
>
  <!-- What It Does -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">What the AI Receptionist Does</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">It's like having a friendly, knowledgeable receptionist who never takes a day off.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Answers Your Phone</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Picks up calls with a natural-sounding voice, greets callers by your business name, and handles conversations like a real person.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Books Appointments</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Connects to your calendar and schedules appointments in real time. No double-booking, no back-and-forth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Answers Questions</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Trained on your business information — hours, services, pricing, location — so callers get accurate answers instantly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Takes Messages</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">When a caller needs to reach you directly, the AI takes a detailed message and sends it to you via text or email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Sends Summaries</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">After every call, you get a text with a summary of what was discussed, who called, and what action was taken.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Works 24/7</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed">Nights, weekends, holidays — your phone always gets answered. No voicemail, no missed opportunities.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-14">How We Set It Up</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shrink-0">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Learn Your Business</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We gather your business info — services, hours, FAQs, scheduling rules — and train the AI on all of it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shrink-0">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Set Up Your Number</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We configure a phone number (or forward your existing one) to the AI receptionist. You choose when it answers — all calls, after-hours, or overflow only.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shrink-0">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Test & Launch</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We test every scenario with you, tweak the responses until they're right, and flip the switch. You start getting call summaries immediately.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who It's For -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-14">Who This Is For</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Small businesses that miss calls during busy hours</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Solo operators who can't answer the phone while working</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Service businesses that need after-hours coverage</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          <p class="text-text-light">Anyone tired of playing phone tag with customers</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
